00:20:28.970 --> 00:20:32.150
As a scholar, indeed,
of questions regarding

00:20:32.150 --> 00:20:34.950
belonging, feeling at home,
nativism, nationalism,

00:20:34.950 --> 00:20:38.780
populism, I love the
