tradition is about equality

00:30:58.470 --> 00:31:01.545
for gender and sexual equality.

00:31:04.800 --> 00:31:07.220
It is, obviously,
then in the dynamic

00:31:07.220 --> 00:31:10.660
of bashing Muslims in the
logic I already explained.

00:31:10.660 --> 00:31:12.860
The third reason why
this is important,

00:31:12.860 --> 00:31:17.060
because it marginalizes
and isolates

00:31:17.060 --> 00:31:19.430
Muslims or religious
minorities at large

00:31:19.430 --> 00:31:21.830
in Western European countries.

00:31:21.830 --> 00:31:24.650
