alien and as if they can never

00:31:24.650 --> 00:31:27.110
become truly Dutch.

00:31:27.110 --> 00:31:29.930
And fourth, this is
important because this

00:31:29.930 --> 00:31:33.875
translates and is part of
a world right polarization.

00:31:33.875 --> 00:31:36.710
A world right
polarization [INAUDIBLE]

00:31:36.710 --> 00:31:41.600
spiraled from two sites,
briefly sketched, very sketchy.

00:31:41.600 --> 00:31:45.470
So the northwestern part
of the world and east south

00:31:45.470 --> 00:31:48.890
part of the world, those
are opposing its order.

00:31:48.890 --> 00:31:50.810
And / most of the
Western countries,

00:31:50.810 --> 00:31:54.740
then, are posing as modern,
and as LGBTI friendly,

00:31:54.740 --> 00:31:58.230
and of course, in favor
of women's rights.

00:31:58.230 --> 00:32:00.950
But they don't frame it
in terms of human rights,

00:32:00.950 --> 00:32:02.270
universal human rights.

00:32:02.270 --> 00:32:04.580
No, those are Western
failures, right?

00:32:04.580 --> 00:32:09.260
And the other side, Eastern
Europe, Russia, the Vatican,

00:32:09.260 --> 00:32:12.180
Muslim majority countries,
they say, yes, you're right,

00:32:12.180 --> 00:32:14.360
those are your values.

00:32:14.360 --> 00:32:16.640
We are proudly disagreeing.

00:32:16.640 --> 00:32:17.880
We are conservative.

00:32:17.880 --> 00:32:19.070
We are traditionals.

00:32:19.070 --> 00:32:21.590
We value family values
in the way we do it.

00:32:21.590 --> 00:32:23.600
And indeed, let's stop
discussing in terms

00:32:23.600 --> 00:32:25.280
of universal human rights.

00:32:25.280 --> 00:32:28.520
So both sides are
reinforcing the idea

00:32:28.520 --> 00:32:32.390
that we have only
very localized values

00:32:32.390 --> 00:32:34.790
and that its roots
should remain like that.

00:32:34.790 --> 00:32:37.050
And therefore, the changes
in those countries,

00:32:37.050 --> 00:32:44.460
so well-discussed this morning,
are so difficult. To conclude,

00:32:44.460 --> 00:32:49.230
what perhaps looks hopeful and
perhaps innocent progressive

00:32:49.230 --> 00:32:50.330
dominance--

00:32:50.330 --> 00:32:53.220
I can imagine you
are dreaming of it--

00:32:53.220 --> 00:32:54.360
has a dark side.

00:32:54.360 --> 00:32:55.290
It has a dark side.

00:32:55.290 --> 00:32:57.180
And we have to realize that.

00:32:57.180 --> 00:32:58.650
It has a dark side
in combination

00:32:58.650 --> 00:33:02.280
with certain forms
of nationalism.

00:33:02.280 --> 00:33:06.150
Because gender and
sexuality are not defined--

00:33:06.150 --> 00:33:09.390
equal rights for
women, for LGBTI--

00:33:09.390 --> 00:33:12.000
anymore in terms of the
universal human rights.

00:33:12.000 --> 00:33:14.070
But only those
parts are supported

00:33:14.070 --> 00:33:16.440
because that's part of
being Dutch, or being

00:33:16.440 --> 00:33:20.130
German, or being Danish.

00:33:20.130 --> 00:33:24.410
When citizenship becomes
dependent on feeling at home

00:33:24.410 --> 00:33:28.140
with just those who are
exactly as progressive,

00:33:28.140 --> 00:33:30.270
how inclusive are we, then?

00:33:30.270 --> 00:33:32.940
I mean, that's the
question we ask ourselves

00:33:32.940 --> 00:33:33.990
