incredible conditions

00:38:14.000 --> 00:38:16.550
to do a PhD at an Ivy
League school and all

00:38:16.550 --> 00:38:21.860
that-- but what was important
was I thought about Turkey

00:38:21.860 --> 00:38:26.090
and I was so sad about how
many resources there were

00:38:26.090 --> 00:38:29.150
and how much of it
was being squandered.

00:38:29.150 --> 00:38:31.700
It was so sad they
didn't exist in Turkey.

00:38:31.700 --> 00:38:35.180
So when I went back to Turkey,
I would be miserable there

00:38:35.180 --> 00:38:37.951
and say, oh my god, there are
all these brilliant people

00:38:37.951 --> 00:38:38.450
here.

00:38:38.450 --> 00:38:40.400
And you know, there
are no resources.

00:38:40.400 --> 00:38:42.720
