after a while

00:38:42.720 --> 00:38:45.620
of living in both societies--

00:38:45.620 --> 00:38:47.910
which I've done
now half and half--

00:38:47.910 --> 00:38:50.460
I don't belong to
any either one.

00:38:50.460 --> 00:38:53.660
